---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="CLI Reference">
  <h1>CLI Reference</h1>

  <h2>Commands</h2>

  <h3>create</h3>
  <p>Create and refine a new agent from a natural language description.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge create "description" [options]

Options:
  --tools {'<list>'}       Comma-separated tools (default: read_file, run_command)
  --output {'<target>'}     Output target: claude-skills or standalone (default: claude-skills)
  --threshold {'<0-1>'}   Pass threshold (default: 0.85)
  --max-iterations {'<N>'} Max refinement iterations (default: 5)</code></pre>
  <p>Example:</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge create "review PRs for logic errors" \
  --tools gh_api,read_file \
  --output claude-skills \
  --threshold 0.85 \
  --max-iterations 5</code></pre>

  <h3>list</h3>
  <p>List all agents in the registry with their latest status.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge list</code></pre>
  <pre><code> Agents (3):

  [PASS] pr_reviewer (v4) — Reviews PRs for logic errors
  [FAIL] code_summarizer (v5) — Summarizes code files
  [NEW]  test_generator (v0) — Generates test cases</code></pre>

  <h3>history</h3>
  <p>Show version history and scores for a specific agent.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge history &lt;name&gt;</code></pre>
  <pre><code> pr_reviewer — 4 version(s):

  v1: score=0.42 pass=no
  v2: score=0.58 pass=no
  v3: score=0.71 pass=no
  v4: score=0.89 pass=yes</code></pre>

  <h3>inspect</h3>
  <p>Inspect the code of a specific agent version.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge inspect &lt;name&gt; [--v N]</code></pre>
  <pre><code># Latest version
agent-forge inspect pr_reviewer

# Specific version
agent-forge inspect pr_reviewer --v 3</code></pre>

  <h3>eval</h3>
  <p>Re-run evaluation against the latest version of an agent.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge eval &lt;name&gt;</code></pre>

  <h3>refine</h3>
  <p>Force a refinement loop starting from the current version.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge refine &lt;name&gt;</code></pre>

  <h3>export</h3>
  <p>Export the latest passed version to a directory.</p>
  <pre><code>agent-forge export &lt;name&gt; --output ./my-agents/</code></pre>

  <h2>Environment Variables</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Variable</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>OLLAMA_BASE_URL</code></td><td>http://localhost:11434</td><td>Ollama server URL</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>OLLAMA_MODEL</code></td><td>llama3.2</td><td>Ollama model name</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code></td><td>—</td><td>OpenAI API key</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code></td><td>—</td><td>Anthropic API key</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>OPENAI_MODEL</code></td><td>gpt-4o</td><td>Model for OpenAI adapter</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>OPENAI_BASE_URL</code></td><td>https://api.openai.com/v1</td><td>API base URL</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>AGENT_FORGE_DATA</code></td><td>.agent-forge</td><td>Data directory</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>AGENT_MAX_DEPTH</code></td><td>3</td><td>Max nested agent call depth</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>AGENT_TIMEOUT_MS</code></td><td>30000</td><td>Per-test execution timeout</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Exit Codes</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Code</th><th>Meaning</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>0</td><td>Success</td></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>Error (LLM unavailable, invalid args, etc.)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>Agent failed to pass quality gate after max iterations</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</Layout>
